<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MovieTrailerApp</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-+0n0xVW2eSR5OomGNYDnhzAbDsOXxcvSN1TPprVMTNDbiYZCxYbOOl7+AMvyTG2x" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-gtEjrD/SeCtmISkJkNUaaKMoLD0//ElJ19smozuHV6z3Iehds+3Ulb9Bn9Plx0x4" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.7.0/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-lZN37f5QGtY3VHgisS14W3ExzMWZxybE1SJSEsQp9S+oqd12jhcu+A56Ebc1zFSJ" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+Pro&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %> 
    
    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="page_title">
          Latest Movie
      </div>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dignissimos sapiente beatae mollitia optio quas, magni fugiat consequatur dolore. Tenetur, exercitationem voluptatibus corporis nemo odio voluptatum pariatur vitae? Qui, incidunt molestiae?<p>
  </div>

    <div class="margin-top margin-bottom">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                 <div class="container"><div class="card bg-dark text-white">
                     <div class="card bg-dark text-white">
                         <% if( latest.poster_path  == null){ %>
                             <img height="400px" src="/img/image-not-found.png" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                         <% } else{ %>
                             <img height="400px" src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/<%- latest.poster_path %>" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                         <% } %>
                     </div>
                 </div>
                 
                 </div>
                 
             </div>
             <div class="col-sm-8">
                 <div class="">
                     <h1><%- latest.original_title %></h2>
                     <div class="movie-single-popularity">
                       <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>  <%- latest.popularity %>
                     </div>
                     <div class="movie-single-vote">
                       Vote : <%- latest.vote_average %> (<%- latest.vote_count %>)
                     </div>
                     <div class="te">
                        <p>Release Date: <%- latest.release_date %></p>
                      </div>
                     <div class="">
                       <p><%- latest.original_title %></p>
                     </div>
                     <div class="">
                       <p><%- latest.overview %></p>
                     </div>
                   </div>
                </div>
             </div>
         </div>  
      
    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>

</body>
</html> 